# Team Effort Tracker -- Streamlit in Snowflake (SiS) App

## Full Technical Summary

**Purpose:** Replaces the Excel-based effort tracker. Allows team members to update task progress daily, gives leads real-time visibility into workload and effort, and supports bulk data import from Excel/CSV.

**Runtime:** Streamlit in Snowflake (SiS) -- runs natively inside Snowflake, no external hosting. Uses Snowpark `get_active_session()` for all DB access.

**Schema:** `DB_CORE_PRD.BACKUP_OPS`

---

