## App Structure -- 3 Tabs

### Tab 1: TASK UPDATES (primary working screen)

- **Add new task form:** Title, Business Reason, Platform/Area (dropdown from existing values + "Other"), Owner (dropdown), Reviewer (dropdown), Start Date, End Date, Status, Effort Days, Completion %, JIRA Reference
- **People dropdowns** built by merging: active TEAM_MEMBERS + distinct OWNER from TASKS + distinct REVIEWER from TASKS. Multi-owner fields like "Alice/Bob" and "Name1 & Name2" are split on `/`, `\`, and `&` so each individual appears separately
- **Existing tasks grouped by owner** as expandable sections. Each owner shows task count (open/closed). Inside, each task has its own expander with: details, progress bar, quick update fields (status/effort/completion), inline note input, action buttons (Save, Edit All, Add Note, Delete)
- **Filters:** Status dropdown, Owner dropdown (individual names after splitting), free text search on title
- **Delete** has 2-step confirmation
- **Edit All** opens inline editing section with all fields
- **Validations:** title required, owner required, start date required, can't close without end date, end date can't precede start date, effort >= 0, completion 0-100, 100% requires Closed status

### Tab 2: TEAM OVERVIEW (read-only for leads)

- **Filters:** Owner, Status, Platform/Area, Start Date range
- **6 metric cards:** Total Tasks, In Progress, Queued, On Hold, Closed, Total Effort (Days)
- **Filtered task data table** with long-running flag (30+ days)
- **4 charts in 2x2 grid** using `st.bar_chart(horizontal=True)`:
  1. Effort by Owner (Days) -- uses exploded owners, effort split evenly between co-owners
  2. Task Status Distribution
  3. Tasks by Platform/Area
  4. Open Tasks per Owner -- stacked by status (In Progress/Queued/On Hold)
- Charts use `_explode_owners()` that splits multi-member OWNER fields and divides effort proportionally

### Tab 3: DATA IMPORT (one-time migration tool)

- Upload CSV or Excel file
- Manual column mapping: 13 fields (Task Title, Business Reason, Platform/Area, Owner, Reviewer, Start Date, End Date, Status, Effort Days, Completion %, JIRA Reference, Comments/Notes)
- Default values for Status and Owner when rows have gaps
- Preview mapped data with validation (flags missing Title/Owner)
- Bulk insert with progress bar
- Comments column inserted as PROGRESS_NOTES entry (tagged "Imported")
- Smart parsing: auto-converts dates, handles decimal completion (0.5 -> 50%), validates status values

