## Technical Details

- **1,200 lines** of Python, single file
- **18 functions** (9 data access, 4 UI helpers, 5 business logic)
- **27 try/except blocks** covering every Snowflake operation with `st.error()` feedback
- **Dark theme:** #0e1117 background, #3b82f6 accent blue, #161b22 cards, all inline CSS via `st.markdown(unsafe_allow_html=True)`
- **No emojis** (SiS resolves emojis through `snowflake.images` schema which may not be authorized)
- **No `page_icon`** in `st.set_page_config`
- **No Google Fonts `@import`** (external URLs blocked in SiS)
- **No `st.dialog()`** (not available in SiS)
- **Session:** `get_active_session()` from `snowflake.snowpark.context`
- **SQL injection mitigation:** `_safe_sql()` escapes single quotes
- **XSS prevention:** `_esc()` HTML-escapes user text in `unsafe_allow_html` blocks
- **Multi-owner handling:** `/` and `&` separators split everywhere. Regex: `r"[/\\&]"`
- **Widget key uniqueness:** keys include `task_id` + `owner_name` to prevent duplicate key errors

