## Known Limitations

1. TEAM_MEMBERS table exists but unused -- people list derived from TASKS data
2. No authentication/role-based access
3. No offline caching
4. Charts use `st.bar_chart(horizontal=True)` with interactive zoom/pan (Vega-Lite) -- considering static matplotlib PNG charts
5. SQL uses string interpolation with `_safe_sql()`, not parameterized queries
6. Team size: ~10-20 people
